---
import Layout from "#layouts/Layout.astro";
import backgroundImage from "#assets/images/background-2.webp";
---

<Layout title="About Us" fullWidth>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-dvh lg:flex-row">
    <div
      class="w-full h-[50vh] sm:h-[60vh] lg:h-auto lg:min-h-screen lg:w-1/2 lg:bg-cover lg:bg-center lg:bg-no-repeat lg:sticky lg:top-0"
      style={`background-image: url('${backgroundImage.src}')`}
    >
      <img
        src={backgroundImage.src}
        alt="Quinoa landscape"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover lg:hidden"
      />
    </div>
    <div
      class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20"
    >
      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto space-y-2 sm:space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h1
            class="text-2xl text-primary sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-start mb-6 sm:mb-8"
          >
            ROOTED IN PERU, CRAFTED WITH CARE.
          </h1>
          <p
            class="text-sm text-secondary font-semibold sm:text-base md:text-lg"
          >
            At <span class="text-accent font-bold">Alefoods,</span> we bring the authentic
            taste of Peru to the world. We specialize in exporting high-quality, natural
            foods, including our select coffee from Oxapampa and ready-to-eat quinoa
            from the Andes. Our mission is to deliver exceptional flavor and nutrition
            while upholding the highest standards of quality and social responsibility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-base text-primary sm:text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-2 sm:mb-3 underline"
          >
            Our Vision
          </h2>
          <p
            class="text-sm font-semibold text-secondary sm:text-base md:text-lg"
          >
            To be recognized nationally and internationally by the most
            demanding markets as a high-quality food exporting company, creating
            well-being for all our customers, suppliers, and collaborators.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-base text-primary sm:text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-2 sm:mb-3 underline"
          >
            Our Mission
          </h2>
          <p
            class="text-sm font-semibold text-secondary sm:text-base md:text-lg"
          >
            To be exporters of food to the world, meeting our customersâ€™ quality
            expectations, caring for the environment, and acting with corporate
            social responsibility.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 sm:mt-6 md:mt-12">
          <a
            href="/products"
            title="View Products"
            aria-label="Explore Our Products"
            class="rounded-lg bg-btn-primary text-light-bg px-6 sm:px-8 md:px-10 py-3 sm:py-4 text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer transition-colors duration-250 ease-in-out border-2 border-filter hover:border-2 hover:border-btn-primary hover:bg-primary disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed"
          >
            Explore Our Products
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
